  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5791",
  "title": "Nested array attributes are not highlighted",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\r\n\r\nI recently swittched from react instantsearch to hooks in hopes of getting rid of the exact issue mentioned here:\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch/issues/2688\r\n\r\nIn short, attributes that are given as nested arrays in the Highlight widget do not get highlighted.\r\n\r\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nAdd a highlight widget to your app like so:\r\n\r\n        <Highlight hit={hit} attribute=\"hierarchy.lvl1\" />\r\n\r\n### Live reproduction\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/nostalgic-diffie-2q54y3\r\n\r\n### 💭 Expected behavior\r\n\r\nAll attributes should get highlighted, even if they are nested arrays.\r\n\r\n### Package version\r\n\r\nreact-instantsearch-hooks-web@6.47.3\r\n\r\n### Operating system\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Browser\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Code of Conduct\r\n\r\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
